critical_fixes.description:
The generated code hardcodes path construction assuming a nested /lineitem/ subdirectory with .col extension. However, GenDB stores all columns in a flat namespace at the root level with names like 'lineitem.l_shipdate.bin'. Update lines 245-251 to use the correct file path pattern:

Current (WRONG):
  ColumnLoader<int32_t> l_shipdate(lineitem_dir + "l_shipdate.col", 60000000);

Correct:
  ColumnLoader<int32_t> l_shipdate(gendb_dir + "/lineitem.l_shipdate.bin", 60000000);

Also update the zone map path from 'lineitem_dir + "l_shipdate.zonemap"' to 'gendb_dir + "/lineitem.l_shipdate.zonemap"'
